OWL semantics
OWL works under the Open World Assumption 
(OWA)
Data Base (Closed World Assumption): the information not 
mentioned is false (Negation as Failure) 
Knowledge Base (Open World Assumption): the information 
not mentioned is unknown (Can be true or false)
